2
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:20,080
EMPAT BELAS BULAN SEBELUM KEBOCORAN GAS

3
00:00:56,280 --> 00:01:00,000
<i>Imad, Carbide membunuhnya.</i>

4
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,400
Membunuhnya.

5
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:07,040
Bagaimana kejadiannya?

6
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,360
Entahlah.

7
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:12,360
Dia sakit saat pulang.

8
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:14,240
Dia terus batuk.

9
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:17,640
Dia bilang ada kebocoran di pabrik...

10
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:18,720
MIC?

11
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,800
<i>Aku tak tahu.</i>

12
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:23,840
<i>Matanya bengkak dan berdarah.</i>

13
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:28,120
<i>Sangat merah seperti diolesi cabai.</i>

14
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:30,040
<i>Matanya sangat perih.</i>

15
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,520
<i>Napasnya berat.</i>

16
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:39,800
Dia terengah-engah dan batuk darah,

17
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,240
seolah-olah paru-parunya meledak.

18
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,720
Kau tahu apa artinya?

19
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,240
Perubahan warna merah ceri?

20
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:03,200
Dia sudah memutuskan akan berhenti.

21
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:08,400
Dia bertahan karena aku.

22
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:12,680
Kupikir kami bisa
menghemat lebih banyak uang...

23
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:16,320
Tidak! Ini sama sekali bukan salahmu!

24
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,400
Uang!

25
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,160
Para bos pabrik pelakunya.

26
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,200
<i>Apa kata bos perusahaan?</i>

27
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,560
Aku disuruh diam.

28
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,960
Tutup mulut.

29
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,760
Bungkam.

30
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,880
Simpanlah.

31
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,720
Untuk Salima...

32
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,880
Untuk kalian berdua.

33
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,520
Pak, baunya seperti almon pahit.

34
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:21,080
Itu dipenuhi racun. Hidrogen sianida.

35
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,880
<i>Aku berjanji...</i>

36
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,240
Aku tak bisa menghidupkan Ansari,

37
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,920
tapi Carbide takkan melupakannya.

