82
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:55,080
KERETA EKSPRES GORAKHPUR

83
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:58,160
Jangan menangis, Sayang.

84
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,680
Salima!

85
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:02,160
Jangan dekat-dekat jendela.
Udaranya dingin.

86
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,400
Kau bisa sakit!

87
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:09,160
Hei, kembali ke sini. Kemari...

88
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:13,480
Dia selalu nakal!

89
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,560
Setiap saat.

90
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,640
Duduklah, dengan tenang.

91
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:27,800
Kau mau, Sayang?

92
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,560
Tidak sopan.

93
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:33,600
Tawari kakak dulu.

94
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:35,960
Kakak mau?

95
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,120
Perutnya sakit.

96
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:43,560
Dia keracunan makanan di Stasiun Jhansi.

97
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,480
Jadi, begitu.

98
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:49,360
Jangan khawatir, Nak. Duduklah di sini.

99
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,640
Ambillah, Nak...

100
00:07:57,720 --> 00:08:00,800
- Bukan hal baru, bukan?
- Maksudnya?

101
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,160
Ayolah, Bung.

102
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:05,800
Kami punya tetangga,
pria Sikh pemilik toko kelontong.

103
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:09,280
Mereka membakar tokonya.
Kenapa? Apa kejahatannya?

104
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:12,640
Karena dia memberi anak-anak permen?

105
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:15,040
Atau dia mengutangi orang membutuhkan?

106
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,720
Keluarganya berantakan dan hancur.

107
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,960
Tapi dia bilang itu bukan hal baru.

108
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:24,280
Bagaimana kau bisa mengatakan itu?
Perdana Menteri dibunuh.

109
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,280
Perdana Menteri, kau mengerti?

110
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:29,320
Amarah perlu dilampiaskan sejenak.
Bukan begitu?

111
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:31,560
- Sejenak?
- Tentu!

112
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:35,080
Sudah lebih dari sebulan,
tapi masih ada insiden.

113
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:38,960
Berhentilah membaca koran.
Siapa suruh membacanya? Kau dipaksa?

114
00:08:39,040 --> 00:08:42,480
Bagus! Aku akan berhenti.
Serta menutup mata dan telingaku.

115
00:08:42,560 --> 00:08:45,120
Tiga ribu orang Sikh dibunuh. Tiga ribu!

116
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:49,320
Begini, "Saat pohon besar tumbang,
tanah di bawahnya bergetar."

117
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,600
- Paham?
- Ya, benar.

118
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:54,360
Dan kau ingin mengguncang
seluruh dunia hari ini?

119
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,520
- Ada penjaga!
- Dengar.

120
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,680
Kecilkan suaramu, jangan berisik.

121
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:01,600
Atau kuturunkan kau
di stasiun berikutnya, paham?

122
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:04,520
Ini kereta api, bukan rumahmu.

123
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:07,120
Dan jika kau pintar, jangan bahas politik.

124
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,200
Itu hanya membuatmu naik darah.

125
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:11,640
Tidurlah. Ayo, waktunya tidur.

126
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,560
Ayo.

127
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:33,520
Ayo, mau duduk semalaman?
Tidurlah. Jangan berisik.

128
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,640
Ayo, waktunya tidur.

129
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:51,480
DUA PULUH MENIT SETELAH KEBOCORAN GAS

130
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,800
EMPLASEMEN NISHATPURA

131
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:55,280
- Aku pergi. Ini kuncinya.
- Oke, aku pergi.

132
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:03,280
Pak, pengerjaan kereta barang selesai.
Kuncinya kuserahkan ke penjaga.

133
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:12,520
Kini, apa selanjutnya?

134
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:15,760
Belum ada. Bersantailah.

135
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:19,880
Saat kru perbaikan komunikasi selesai,

136
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,680
kita harus antar mereka
dari sisi lain stasiun.

137
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:25,000
Bersantailah sambil menunggu.

138
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:30,480
Sialan! Udaranya dingin sekali.

139
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,560
Kenapa tertawa?

140
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,160
Berikan senternya.

141
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,400
Nyalakan.

142
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:41,640
Bagus!

143
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,960
- Sebentar.
- Baik.

144
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:35,800
<i>Para penumpang, mohon perhatian,</i>

145
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:38,360
<i>Kereta Ekspress Gorakhpur 82 Utara
akan tiba...</i>

146
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:41,600
Kaamil seharusnya menjemput kita
tiga jam lalu!

147
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:44,120
Seharusnya kita sudah beristirahat
di pondok!

148
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:47,520
Adil, tenanglah, Nak.
Cuma soal waktu. Ini akan berlalu.

149
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:51,200
Tidak. Sia-sia aku kemari setiap tahun.

150
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:53,480
Saat kau akhirnya
mempelajari makna Ijtima,

151
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:55,360
belajar sabar, maka kau takkan datang.

152
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:57,960
Bhairavi, kau menonton kriket?

153
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,680
Bahkan Gavaskar kadang melempar.

154
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:04,520
Tapi di tim kita,
bahkan perenang tak bisa berenang.

155
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,800
"Tolong! Aku tak bisa bernapas!"

156
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:10,080
Cukup! Jangan keterlaluan!

157
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:15,160
Nona-Nona, tak perlu kesal.

158
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,320
Menang dan kalah biasa di olahraga.

159
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,760
Ayolah, jangan sedih! Kalian hebat.

160
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:24,560
Posisi kedua. Kau hebat.

161
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,640
Ulurkan kakimu.

162
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,120
- Kak?
- Ya?

163
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:42,360
Ingat lagu pengantar tidur
yang dinyanyikan Ibu?

164
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,240
Kau ingat lagunya?

165
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,760
Kau ingat melodinya?

166
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:49,640
- Aku yakin kau ingat...
- Tidak.

167
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,320
Kaki satunya.

168
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:03,040
- Pak!
- Ya? Bukan aku! Dia di sana!

169
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,720
- Pak!
- Ada masalah apa, Vijaya?

170
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:07,400
Pak, masalahnya...

171
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:10,840
Keluarga mempelai pria
kedatangan tamu tak diundang.

172
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:11,880
Oke, lalu?

173
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,120
Kami akan kehabisan makanan.

174
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:19,360
Katering meminta 350 rupee lagi.
Kalau tidak, dia takkan melayani mereka.

175
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:23,160
- Aku tak punya uang lagi.
- Itu bukan masalah.

176
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,640
Semua uangku sudah habis.

177
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:30,000
- Ambil ini.
- Akan segera kuganti, Pak.

178
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:34,240
Ini 270 rupee. Kuberikan sisanya besok.

179
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,960
Dia akan menutup dapur, Pak.

180
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:40,040
Dia tak boleh menutup...

181
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,040
Kau punya 80 rupee?

182
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:44,560
- Pak?
- Kau punya 80 rupee?

183
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:45,960
Ya, tentu saja.

184
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:51,560
Apa pun untuk sesama pegawai Kereta Api!

185
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:53,440
Ini bonus Diwali-ku. Ambillah.

186
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,240
Akan segera kukembalikan.

187
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:57,000
Tenang saja. Cepatlah kembali.

188
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,840
- Terberkatilah kau!
- Terima kasih.

189
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:01,520
Dua puluh rupee sisanya... Aku...

190
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:04,200
- Terima kasih. Tolong tutup pintunya.
- Oke.

191
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:10,040
Apa-apan aku ini?

192
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:22,080
Bung? Kenapa dia?

193
00:14:22,680 --> 00:14:23,840
Lihat dia.

194
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:29,760
Ada apa?

195
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:32,000
Pak Sharma, ada apa? Bangun!

196
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,360
Tak bisa bernapas!

197
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:50,960
Sialan! Bau apa ini?

198
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:02,800
Hei!

199
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,920
Hei, Nak!

200
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,360
Hei, Nak!

201
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:12,000
Bau apa ini? Kau menciumnya juga?

202
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:16,280
Bau kol rebus!

203
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,000
Kak Sohini!

204
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:41,280
- Ada apa?
- Seorang tamu...

205
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:44,560
<i>Amma</i>! Bibi, di mana <i>Amma</i>?

206
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:45,600
Lari!

207
00:15:45,680 --> 00:15:48,200
Ibumu pergi ke stasiun
untuk meminjam uang.

208
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:51,240
Bangun, Nak. Buka matamu.

209
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:59,080
- Hei!
- Minggir! Aku mau lewat!

210
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:02,440
Pak?

211
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:04,240
Pak!

212
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:14,520
- Tinggalkan semuanya, lari!
- Lari!

213
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:16,200
- Keluar dari sini!
- Cepat keluar!

214
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,440
Udaranya beracun!

215
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,480
Aku sesak napas!

216
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:22,800
Hei, tunggu aku...

217
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:26,040
Kenapa kuda ini?

218
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,960
Udaranya beracun.

219
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,120
Aku tak bisa bernapas...

220
00:16:45,040 --> 00:16:48,280
- Ikut denganku!
- Aku pergi dari sini. Pergilah!

221
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:54,080
Air... Ambilkan aku air.

222
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:59,280
Paman! Ikut aku. Berdiri, ayo.

223
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:05,680
Bibi! Keluar dan larilah!

224
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:07,400
- Cepat!
- Tapi Imad?

225
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:09,800
Tanpa Imad...

226
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,760
Ayo. Duduk di sini.

227
00:17:26,560 --> 00:17:27,480
Perkampungan!

228
00:17:27,560 --> 00:17:30,960
Bawa aku ke sana.
Keluargaku masih di sana.

229
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:37,320
Cepat pergi dari sini!

